Elvis & Nixon is a 2016 American comedy-drama film directed by Liza Johnson and written by Joey Sagal , Hanala Sagal , and Cary Elwes .
The film stars Kevin Spacey as President Richard Nixon and Michael Shannon as singer Elvis Presley , and focuses on the December 21 , 1970 meeting between the two men at the White House .
The film also stars Alex Pettyfer , Johnny Knoxville , Colin Hanks , and Evan Peters .
The film was released on April 22 , 2016 by Amazon Studios and Bleecker Street .